"**ROT**, **SOG**, **STW**, **TWA**, **TWD**, **TWS**, **WTEMP**. If a data "
"type is selected for OneValue display that only allows a numeric display, "
"the ``[MODE]`` and ``[ZOOM]`` keys will not be available."

